<h2 style="color: #28a745;">Welcome to Haat Bazaar</h2>
<p>Nepal trusted partner in healthy living and farm fresh produce. We are more than just an online grocery store we are a movement toward a healthier, more sustainable lifestyle, powered by nature and delivered with care.</p>
<p>We are a passionate team of farmers, nutrition enthusiasts, logisticians, and tech experts who believe that everyone deserves access to fresh, high-quality fruits and vegetables, no matter where they live. What started as a small initiative to deliver produce in our local community has grown into a nationwide service, connecting hundreds of households with trusted local growers every day.</p>
<p>Our team is united by one goal: to make healthy living convenient and affordable for all Nepali families.</p>
<p>We specialize in delivering:</p>
<ul>
<li>Fresh seasonal fruits apples, bananas, mangoes, oranges, and more</li>
<li>Organic and local vegetables</li>
<li>Exotic produce, herbs, and farm grown items</li>
<li>Customized fruit baskets for homes, offices, or special occasions</li>
<li>Every item is carefully selected, washed, packed, and delivered to ensure premium quality, hygiene, and flavor.</li>
</ul>
